{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-templates-blog-post-source-github-js","path":"/2019-06-30-site-settings/","webpackCompilationHash":"c21d7181b101d039822a","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"suzukalight.com","author":"suzukalight"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5f9e575f-3bbf-51f7-8d89-39db9f14de3f","excerpt":"Gatsbyのプラグインを利用することで、ブログに必要な数々の設定を簡単におこなうことができた。 PWA対応 Add manifest and favicon  が利用可能。starter…","html":"<p>Gatsbyのプラグインを利用することで、ブログに必要な数々の設定を簡単におこなうことができた。</p>\n<h1 id=\"pwa対応\"><a href=\"#pwa%E5%AF%BE%E5%BF%9C\" aria-label=\"pwa対応 permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PWA対応</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/suzukalight/suzukalight.github.io/commit/13b7d4660c560061a3892daa54e76b89162cb2ef\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Add manifest and favicon</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-manifest</code> が利用可能。starterで自動インストール済み。</p>\n<p>マニフェストの内容とアイコン類は、下記のサイトを使って自動生成することができる。それを <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> にコピペすれば良い。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>手順: <a href=\"https://takumon.com/2018/10/08/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://takumon.com/2018/10/08/</a></li>\n<li>生成: <a href=\"https://app-manifest.firebaseapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://app-manifest.firebaseapp.com/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"ogp対応\"><a href=\"#ogp%E5%AF%BE%E5%BF%9C\" aria-label=\"ogp対応 permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>OGP対応</h1>\n<p>starter に付属のコンポーネント <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;SEO /&gt;</code> を利用すると、多くの項目について、自動でOGPを設定してくれるため、こちらから追加で何かをする必要はほとんどなかった。</p>\n<h1 id=\"テーマ変更\"><a href=\"#%E3%83%86%E3%83%BC%E3%83%9E%E5%A4%89%E6%9B%B4\" aria-label=\"テーマ変更 permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>テーマ変更</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/suzukalight/suzukalight.github.io/commit/976447b1a6b7cdeb3a6fd60b6ba8663f8174321b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Add typography theme of github</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>starterは <a href=\"https://kyleamathews.github.io/typography.js/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">typography.js</a> で文字のスタイリングを行っている。typographyjsのテーマにGitHub版の <code class=\"language-text\">typography-theme-github</code> があったので、これを適用した。</p>\n<h1 id=\"目次の追加\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%AE%E6%AC%A1%E3%81%AE%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0\" aria-label=\"目次の追加 permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>目次の追加</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-transformer-remark/#getting-table-of-contents\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">getting-table-of-contents</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>queryに<code class=\"language-text\">tableOfContents</code>を追加すると、目次情報のHTMLを取得することができる；</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">templates/BlogPost/index.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight has-highlighted-lines\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> pageQuery <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> graphql<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  query BlogPostBySlug($slug: String!) {\n    markdownRemark(fields: { slug: { eq: $slug } }) {\n      html\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">      tableOfContents</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>あとはこれをマークアップしつつ表示すればOK；</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>section className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>toc<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1 className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tocHeader<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>目次<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div\n    className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tocBody<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    dangerouslySetInnerHTML<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> __html<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> post<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tableOfContents <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>section<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"syntax-highlighter\"><a href=\"#syntax-highlighter\" aria-label=\"syntax highlighter permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>syntax-highlighter</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/suzukalight/suzukalight.github.io/commit/ed08bb35190bbb2bea121af2a0cedfddff6388a8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Add syntax highligher</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-remark-prismjs</code> のオプションで指定可能。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/suzukalight/suzukalight.github.io/commit/91aeab5e033a4f8001d363ddf88dd538f80c8e1f\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Add gatsby-remark-code-titles</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-remark-code-titles</code> を追加すると、さらにファイル名表記も付与可能に。</p>\n<h1 id=\"google-analytics\"><a href=\"#google-analytics\" aria-label=\"google analytics permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Google Analytics</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-plugin-google-analytics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">gatsby-plugin-google-analytics</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>プラグイン自体は、すでにstarterに入っています。<code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>を書き換えるだけでOKです；</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-config.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight has-highlighted-lines\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-google-analytics</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">    trackingId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'YOUR TRACKING ID'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></span>  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"rss-feed\"><a href=\"#rss-feed\" aria-label=\"rss feed permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>RSS Feed</h1>\n<p>starterでデフォルト有効です。<code class=\"language-text\">/rss.xml</code> で配信されます。</p>\n<h1 id=\"sitemap\"><a href=\"#sitemap\" aria-label=\"sitemap permalink\" class=\"gatsby-autolink-headers\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sitemap</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-plugin-sitemap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">gatsby-plugin-sitemap</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>sitemapプラグインをインストールし、サイト情報とオプションを設定すればOKです；</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">gatsby-config.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight has-highlighted-lines\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">siteMetadata<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">  siteUrl<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://suzukalight.com</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-sitemap</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></span><span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></span><span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">      sitemapSize<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></span><span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\">    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></span>  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#pwa%E5%AF%BE%E5%BF%9C\">PWA対応</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#ogp%E5%AF%BE%E5%BF%9C\">OGP対応</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#%E3%83%86%E3%83%BC%E3%83%9E%E5%A4%89%E6%9B%B4\">テーマ変更</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#%E7%9B%AE%E6%AC%A1%E3%81%AE%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0\">目次の追加</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#syntax-highlighter\">syntax-highlighter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#google-analytics\">Google Analytics</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#rss-feed\">RSS Feed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2019-06-30-site-settings/#sitemap\">Sitemap</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby のサイトカスタマイズ","date":"2019-06-30T00:08:00","description":"PWA対応・OGP対応・テーマ変更・目次表示・syntaxHighlight・GA設定・RSS・Sitemap","category":"Technology","tags":["gatsby","pwa"],"hero":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":2,"src":"/static/1942d23e2373e55eef308f459fa50d8a/e95fb/gatsbyjs.jpg","srcSet":"/static/1942d23e2373e55eef308f459fa50d8a/f0922/gatsbyjs.jpg 320w,\n/static/1942d23e2373e55eef308f459fa50d8a/8d58c/gatsbyjs.jpg 640w,\n/static/1942d23e2373e55eef308f459fa50d8a/e95fb/gatsbyjs.jpg 1280w,\n/static/1942d23e2373e55eef308f459fa50d8a/27e28/gatsbyjs.jpg 1440w","sizes":"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"source":"github","slug":"/2019-06-30-site-settings/","previous":{"head":{"title":"Gatsby + GitHub Pages でブログを構築","category":"Technology","tags":["gatsby","github pages","react"],"date":"2019-06-29T23:11:00","slug":"/2019-06-29-hello-world/","source":"github"},"siteMetadata":{"title":"suzukalight.com"}},"next":{"head":{"title":"Gatsby のファイル構成","category":"Technology","tags":["gatsby"],"date":"2019-07-01T23:00:00","slug":"/2019-07-01-file-structure/","source":"github"},"siteMetadata":{"title":"suzukalight.com"}}}}}